OL,3,CArts gallery reverses decision to
OL,4,Ccancel Palestinian exhibition after
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FAn arts gallery has reversed its
OL,8,Fdecision to cancel their Palestinian
OL,9,Farts show after protests sparked
OL,10,Fdozens of artists in removing their
OL,11,Fwork from the venue.
OL,13,FThe HOME Arts Venue in planned to host
OL,14,Fa Voice of Resilience exhibition on 22
OL,15,FApril 2024, before deciding to cancel
OL,16,Fthe event in response to a letter from
OL,17,Fa local Jewish Representative Council.
OL,19,FIt is understood HOME cancelled the
OL,20,Farts show with the aim to remain
OL,21,F'politically neutral'.
