OL,7,FWhile taking down their artworks,
OL,8,Fartists displayed copies of a
OL,9,Fstatement calling for an apology from
OL,10,FHOME and the reinstatement of the
OL,11,Fexhibition, as well as demanding a
OL,12,Fforum for "Palestinians and their
OL,13,Fallies" to raise concerns.
OL,15,FDani Abulhawa, British-Palestinian
OL,16,Fartist and curator of the event, said:
OL,17,F"Venues should not shy away from the
OL,18,Fchallenges of presenting work that
OL,19,Ftouches on geo-politics and should
OL,20,Ffoster safe, critical spaces where
OL,21,Fdifferent perspectives can be seen."
