OL,7,FIn a statement, HOME says the initial
OL,8,Fdecision to cancel Voices of
OL,9,FResilience was difficult.
OL,11,FHOME said: "We recognise how deeply
OL,12,Fthis decision has affected communities
OL,13,Fand groups across Manchester and
OL,14,Fbeyond, and we apologise for any
OL,15,Fdistress or upset caused.
OL,17,F"We support Palestinian and all
OL,18,Fcommunity voices, and acknowledge that
OL,19,Fwe can learn from how this was
OL,20,Fhandled. We regret that this has had
OL,21,Fsuch wide-reaching impacts.
