OL,7,F"Since our initial statement, we have
OL,8,Fcontinued to collaborate and consult
OL,9,Fwith stakeholders and the artists
OL,10,Finvolved, and to review and develop
OL,11,Fplans.
OL,13,F"We have reached out to partners in
OL,14,Fthe city for assistance and have been
OL,15,Fable to access additional resources
OL,16,Fthat will support us delivering the
OL,17,Fevent.
