OL,7,F"This commitment has never changed,
OL,8,Fand we recognise that there is work to
OL,9,Fbe done now, to restore the well-
OL,10,Fearned confidence that our audiences
OL,11,Fand artists have always held in HOME.
OL,13,F"We are committed to continuing these
OL,14,Fconversations with all affected by
OL,15,Frecent events."
OL,17,FHOME will announce the details of the
OL,18,Fevent shortly.
